Description: The NYSTAR Annual meeting will feature three unique venues during the two day event. Today we will begin the meeting at Coltivare Culinary Center, 235 S. Cayuga Street, Ithaca located across the street from Hotel Ithaca. If you need parking – there is a parking garage behind the building. The evening reception will take place at REV Ithaca Startup Works, walking distance from Coltivare and the Hotel Ithaca. Parking is very limited.
